{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "ecomkassa-api-collection",
		"name": "EcomKassa API",
		"description": "Коллекция для тестирования API шлюза EcomKassa\n\nБазовый URL: https://gw.ecomkassa.ru\n\nШаги использования:\n1. Получить AuthToken через CreateAuthToken\n2. Использовать токен в других запросах\n3. Создать чек через /receipt\n4. Проверить статус через /status",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
	"item": [
		{
			"name": "1. Authorization",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "Create Auth Token",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"// Автоматически сохраняем токен в переменные окружения",
									"if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
									"    const jsonData = pm.response.json();",
									"    if (jsonData.AuthToken) {",
									"        pm.environment.set('authToken', jsonData.AuthToken);",
									"        console.log('AuthToken сохранён:', jsonData.AuthToken);",
									"    }",
									"}"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"Login\": \"{{login}}\",\n  \"Password\": \"{{password}}\"\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/Authorization/CreateAuthToken",
							"host": [
								"{{baseUrl}}"
							],
							"path": [
								"api",
								"Authorization",
								"CreateAuthToken"
							]
						},
						"description": "Получение токена авторизации для дальнейших запросов.\n\nПараметры:\n- Login: логин кассы\n- Password: пароль кассы\n\nОтвет содержит AuthToken, который автоматически сохраняется в переменные окружения."
					},
					"response": [
						{
							"name": "Success",
							"originalRequest": {
								"method": "POST",
								"header": [],
								"body": {
									"mode": "raw",
									"raw": "{\n  \"Login\": \"test_login\",\n  \"Password\": \"test_password\"\n}",
									"options": {
										"raw": {
											"language": "json"
										}
									}
								},
								"url": {
									"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/Authorization/CreateAuthToken",
									"host": [
										"{{baseUrl}}"
									],
									"path": [
										"api",
										"Authorization",
										"CreateAuthToken"
									]
								}
							},
							"status": "OK",
							"code": 200,
							"_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
							"header": [
								{
									"key": "Content-Type",
									"value": "application/json"
								}
							],
							"cookie": [],
							"body": "{\n  \"AuthToken\": \"example_token_12345\",\n  \"Errors\": null\n}"
						}
					]
				}
			],
			"description": "Эндпоинты для авторизации"
		},
		{
			"name": "2. KKT Operations",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "Get KKT Status",
					"request": {
						"method": "GET",
						"header": [],
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/kkt/cloud/status?uuid={{kkt_uuid}}&AuthToken={{authToken}}",
							"host": [
								"{{baseUrl}}"
							],
							"path": [
								"api",
								"kkt",
								"cloud",
								"status"
							],
							"query": [
								{
									"key": "uuid",
									"value": "{{kkt_uuid}}",
									"description": "UUID кассы"
								},
								{
									"key": "AuthToken",
									"value": "{{authToken}}",
									"description": "Токен авторизации (автоматически подставляется)"
								}
							]
						},
						"description": "Получение статуса кассы по UUID.\n\nПараметры:\n- uuid: UUID кассы\n- AuthToken: токен авторизации (автоматически подставляется из переменных)\n\nОтвет содержит информацию о состоянии кассы."
					},
					"response": [
						{
							"name": "Success",
							"originalRequest": {
								"method": "GET",
								"header": [],
								"url": {
									"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/kkt/cloud/status?uuid=test-uuid-123&AuthToken=test_token",
									"host": [
										"{{baseUrl}}"
									],
									"path": [
										"api",
										"kkt",
										"cloud",
										"status"
									],
									"query": [
										{
											"key": "uuid",
											"value": "test-uuid-123"
										},
										{
											"key": "AuthToken",
											"value": "test_token"
										}
									]
								}
							},
							"status": "OK",
							"code": 200,
							"_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
							"header": [
								{
									"key": "Content-Type",
									"value": "application/json"
								}
							],
							"cookie": [],
							"body": "{\n  \"Status\": \"ready\",\n  \"CheckNumber\": 42,\n  \"SessionNumber\": 15,\n  \"Errors\": null\n}"
						}
					]
				},
				{
					"name": "Create Receipt",
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"AuthToken\": \"{{authToken}}\",\n  \"Request\": {\n    \"UUID\": \"{{kkt_uuid}}\",\n    \"Request\": {\n      \"Type\": \"Income\",\n      \"InvoiceId\": \"{{$randomUUID}}\",\n      \"TaxationType\": \"OSN\",\n      \"ClientInfo\": {\n        \"EmailOrPhone\": \"+79001234567\"\n      },\n      \"Items\": [\n        {\n          \"Price\": 100.00,\n          \"Quantity\": 1,\n          \"Amount\": 100.00,\n          \"Name\": \"Тестовый товар\",\n          \"Tax\": \"NDS20\",\n          \"PaymentMethod\": \"FullPayment\",\n          \"PaymentObject\": \"Commodity\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"Cash\": 0.00,\n      \"ElectronicPayment\": 100.00,\n      \"AdvancePayment\": 0.00,\n      \"Credit\": 0.00,\n      \"CashProvision\": 0.00\n    }\n  }\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/kkt/cloud/receipt",
							"host": [
								"{{baseUrl}}"
							],
							"path": [
								"api",
								"kkt",
								"cloud",
								"receipt"
							]
						},
						"description": "Создание нового чека.\n\nТело запроса содержит:\n- AuthToken: токен авторизации (автоматически подставляется)\n- Request.UUID: UUID кассы\n- Request.Request: данные чека (тип, товары, сумма и т.д.)\n\nОтвет содержит информацию о созданном чеке."
					},
					"response": [
						{
							"name": "Success",
							"originalRequest": {
								"method": "POST",
								"header": [],
								"body": {
									"mode": "raw",
									"raw": "{\n  \"AuthToken\": \"test_token\",\n  \"Request\": {\n    \"UUID\": \"test-uuid-123\",\n    \"Request\": {\n      \"Type\": \"Income\",\n      \"InvoiceId\": \"invoice-123\",\n      \"TaxationType\": \"OSN\",\n      \"ClientInfo\": {\n        \"EmailOrPhone\": \"+79001234567\"\n      },\n      \"Items\": [\n        {\n          \"Price\": 100.00,\n          \"Quantity\": 1,\n          \"Amount\": 100.00,\n          \"Name\": \"Тестовый товар\",\n          \"Tax\": \"NDS20\",\n          \"PaymentMethod\": \"FullPayment\",\n          \"PaymentObject\": \"Commodity\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"Cash\": 0.00,\n      \"ElectronicPayment\": 100.00\n    }\n  }\n}",
									"options": {
										"raw": {
											"language": "json"
										}
									}
								},
								"url": {
									"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/kkt/cloud/receipt",
									"host": [
										"{{baseUrl}}"
									],
									"path": [
										"api",
										"kkt",
										"cloud",
										"receipt"
									]
								}
							},
							"status": "OK",
							"code": 200,
							"_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
							"header": [
								{
									"key": "Content-Type",
									"value": "application/json"
								}
							],
							"cookie": [],
							"body": "{\n  \"CheckNumber\": 43,\n  \"SessionNumber\": 15,\n  \"FiscalSign\": \"1234567890\",\n  \"Errors\": null\n}"
						}
					]
				}
			],
			"description": "Операции с кассой (статус, создание чеков)"
		},
